ShortJS: A Lightweight JavaScript Library

ShortJS is a lightweight JavaScript library designed to streamline and simplify code, making development tasks more efficient and concise. Whether you're a seasoned developer or just starting out, ShortJS offers a collection of utility functions and shortcuts to help you write cleaner, more expressive code.

With ShortJS, you can:

- Reduce repetitive code by leveraging concise utility functions.
- Improve readability by abstracting complex logic into simple, reusable snippets.
- Enhance productivity by speeding up development time with intuitive shortcuts and helpers.

ShortJS is released under the MIT License, allowing developers to use it freely in their projects, whether personal or commercial. By incorporating ShortJS into your codebase, you can optimize your workflow and focus on building great software without sacrificing simplicity or flexibility.

Get started with ShortJS today and experience the power of streamlined JavaScript development. Happy coding!